                    <h3>mySpoons and dailySpoons</h3>
                        <p>
                        mySpoons and dailySpoons are simple, daily apps that make planning easier by using quantities of spoons 
                        as a way to measure your energy.  Users can plan the amount of energy they will use in a day and see how 
                        it compares with the maximum energy use that they've set for themselves.  mySpoons and dailySpoons enable 
                        chronically ill or disabled users to engage in life and manage health conditions.   
                        </p>
